text: == Falęcin, Kuyavian-Pomeranian Voivodeship == Falęcin [faˈlɛnt͡ɕin] (German: Dietrichsdorf) is a village in the administrative district of Gmina Papowo Biskupie, within Chełmno County, Kuyavian-Pomeranian Voivodeship, in north- central Poland. It lies approximately 4 kilometres (2 mi) south of Papowo Biskupie, 19 km (12 mi) south-east of Chełmno, and 21 km (13 mi) north of Toruń. Category:Villages in Kuyavian-Pomeranian Voivodeship
title: Falęcin, Kuyavian-Pomeranian Voivodeship
